      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s640x960/d68102104af8a1e5463f612bc64759d82893a611.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"1034\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Three cool scientists introduce their work &quot;Our new theory has been submitted to a peer-reviewed journal, but we feel its depths and intricacies are best appreciated on the limited-edition vinyl release.&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s75x75_c1/2bfa74b534a0b0093ede35b78d239580e8334162.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s100x200/1a6ecbd3f38a23e951110a45614fbef82896bc1e.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s250x400/c5322b0bebaf1b6b269ab4675b9f042f705829ea.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s400x600/d1ecbf32c0d939f368737eb4296652f5a7196cf1.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s500x750/4629bbe697b25c8e3f7bad1a73b65b86ea839d04.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s540x810/7adea4b3331b302f08848b1f19e786a3019ef2db.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s640x960/d68102104af8a1e5463f612bc64759d82893a611.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s1280x1920/e2737e140b29b917508112bdb8d12e96bc6c2d0f.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cedc984c277a6833296c5ad59aff4dfd/c6fba2a9476c1ecb-e7/s2048x3072/c4837538083778ee2d539cb3dd2bfce229b6905e.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
